WEBVTT

00:00:09.926 --> 00:00:18.768 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With the days forever darkening
And the signs so very clear,

00:00:18.768 --> 00:00:28.011 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We must keep our sense of urgency
As the end is drawing near.

00:00:28.011 --> 00:00:36.986 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We will seize this opportunity
To declare Jehovah’s name,

00:00:36.986 --> 00:00:44.961 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And the blessings of his Kingdom
Is the message we’ll proclaim.

00:00:44.961 --> 00:00:49.499 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now is the time
For preaching with zeal.

00:00:49.499 --> 00:00:53.970 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll never give up
or give way to fear.

00:00:53.970 --> 00:00:58.241 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And now is the time
To show how we feel,

00:00:58.241 --> 00:01:06.616 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now that the final days are here.

00:01:08.251 --> 00:01:16.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There will never be another time
For this preaching to be done.

00:01:16.659 --> 00:01:25.502 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So we want to have a part in it
And reach out to ev’ryone.

00:01:25.502 --> 00:01:34.677 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When we look back in some future time
At these days in which we live,

00:01:34.677 --> 00:01:43.119 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then we’ll say that for Jehovah
We gave all that we could give.

00:01:43.119 --> 00:01:47.557 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now is the time
For preaching with zeal.

00:01:47.557 --> 00:01:51.694 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll never give up
or give way to fear.

00:01:51.694 --> 00:01:56.132 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And now is the time
To show how we feel,

00:01:56.132 --> 00:02:04.474 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now that the final days are here.

00:02:10.613 --> 00:02:19.722 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
With our loyal ones surrounding us
We will run with all our might.

